"SERPENT KICK"

Usage: serpent <victim>

This punishing, lethal kick is part of the Golden Serpent Kung Fu style, and
knowledge of it is forbidden outside the Liu'she Ch'uan tong. Learning it
earns a sentence of death from any tong member. Beware.

