#
"TIGER PUNCH" TIGER

Usage: tiger <victim>

This devastating uppercut can do serious damage to the victim if they are unable
to block it.  The tiger punch is a more aggressive style of ninja combat, used 
when the ninja cannot avoid direct confrontation.

